These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, rat, frog, horse
1. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the horse##2
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Pet   | fish | horse | rat | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, wooden, ranch-style
1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
2. the wooden house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the ranch-style house is between the cape-cod house and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| House   | cape-cod | ranch-style | gothic-revival | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
City: liverpool, san-francisco, hamburg, london
1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person traveling to london##2
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| City   | liverpool | london | hamburg | san-francisco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, skiing, surfing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is basketball##2
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Sport   | weightlifting | skiing | surfing | basketball |

 #################################

 
