.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, blood-red, ivory, fuchsia
1. the person who likes coral is between the person who likes ivory and the person who likes blood-red##2
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Color   | ivory | coral | blood-red | fuchsia |

 